{"tid":1910514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【血饅】掟鳩人包個葉子祈 出聲明冇道歉","createTime":"2020-03-04T17:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T08:48:50.000Z","uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a93dab15be05530dc8b1a56effdaa3729aec00","tid":1910514,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:16:51.000Z","msg":"點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CtLOgs0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtLOgs0.jpg&h=1d2ad4dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104701190869887/posts/199011234772215/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104701190869887%2Fposts%2F199011234772215%2F&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=60dae356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104701190869887/posts/199011234772215/</a>"},{"pid":"9f4dd5ce49497f19951462e1b1c40402daf55479","tid":1910514,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:17:38.000Z","msg":"補返張圖 驚大家唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DYM2dHR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDYM2dHR.gif&h=9ee9c58e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c525bd413b570741f7d356f9ef901ffb763ba0b7","tid":1910514,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:18:40.000Z","msg":"「<span style=\"color: red;\">葉議員的憤怒，何以為過</span>」<br />\n<br />\n仲死唔認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e682be80d258d74c265a90edb10dd0ab0fa9b734","tid":1910514,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:21:05.000Z","msg":"原來掟鳩人人血饅頭係咁正當嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e030103b9c400d05a1a0619a923a49609d7f3dd","tid":1910514,"uid":69707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:22:13.000Z","msg":"葉公好龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efaf33919b5a978d3b0f6320a3b04f03c6ac3bfa","tid":1910514,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"俾我係柯耀林就報驚拉鳩條柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7cefe2b9fbfcc766c956f0c6d6e89e98575d54","tid":1910514,"uid":236414,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:22:39.000Z","msg":"關於將民組<br />\n<br />\n佢可以先徵詢家人意見，同埋問過公園當區區議員（係呀即係葉子祈呀，調景嶺公園喺嗰句㗎），之後先拎上會；佢通通唔做，仲話已經拎到家人同意呃咗其中一個和議返嚟但原來又唔係<br />\n<br />\n提案嘅將民組又話要尊重家人意願，又話唔駛問佢屋企人，我睇佢地啲point睇到我就嚟精神分裂喇你知唔知呀？咁嘅情況下，將民組唔單止唔肯收回議案，仲要喺網台度話「反對嘅都係收咗錢，係共產黨」，即係明明開波嘈交嗰個都係將民組喎<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n關於人血饅頭<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳遊行嗰陣，將民組走嚟帶頭set條路線經過晒自己啲選區最後入TVB，當正係自己選舉遊行咁款，呢啲直頭係人血饅頭到人贓並鑊嗰隻。<br />\n<br />\n今次呢個議案由陸平才同柯耀林提出，和議嘅只得自己友 + 蔡明禧，然後其他人完全唔知亦都無問過突然拎出嚟，如果呢個議案通過咗，佢地就係成功爭取，益晒自己友；通過唔到嘅，就話反對嘅都係共產黨，然後又係話自己腹背受敵，扮慘，咁又搏到選票喇喎。唔知柯耀林今次出山，會唔會劍指立法會呢？<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，個個都係食咗人血饅頭先至會入到議會，但食相咁難睇，係將民組嘅專利嚟。你話街坊私怨都係咁話，將民組界票界得咁開心就以為自己想點都得，就可以冼人一鑊呀？<br />\n<br />\n屌緊西貢區議會既人究竟知唔知.......<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ozwujMX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ozwujMX</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋係專門博出位 罔顧其他議員勸止堅持提議案 五區界同路人界票 反送中議案投棄權票 搬走路障 保送方國珊入議會 師承劉慧卿鄭家富嘅將軍澳饅頭關注組<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/p5Htgn4.png\" />"},{"pid":"ec06cde0a460cb3bf8b55a3a9077d24c1a19929e","tid":1910514,"uid":11049,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"葉子祈無做錯點解要道歉"},{"pid":"c6e8e3b5c40f7df34ef130a053538572d469c0df","tid":1910514,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"食屎祈"},{"pid":"41e96f870ee2ab2723f421ad3c3f327a9bc6b352","tid":1910514,"uid":95138,"like":0,"